WEBVTT

00:02.840 --> 00:04.680
The will was sent back to the capital

00:05.200 --> 00:06.880
Xie Xuan was ordered to assist in governance

00:07.720 --> 00:10.400
Crown Prince Sikong Sheng successfully ascended the throne

00:10.880 --> 00:12.920
Posthumously titled you as Emperor Xuancheng

00:13.280 --> 00:16.360
And changed the era name to Taian the following year

00:27.920 --> 00:29.280
After Sikong Sheng ascended the throne

00:29.440 --> 00:31.600
Although nominally the ruler of all under heaven

00:32.120 --> 00:35.880
The army still had many remnants of Sikong Xu's faction

00:36.120 --> 00:37.960
Threatening the state's stability

00:38.880 --> 00:43.000
Grand General Zhu Yuanzhi, in the name of intimidating border tribes

00:43.280 --> 00:45.280
Stationed troops at the Yan Bei border

00:46.160 --> 00:46.600
Regarding this

00:46.920 --> 00:49.480
Sikong Sheng adopted a strategy of divide and conquer

00:50.240 --> 00:50.640
On one hand

00:51.000 --> 00:52.560
Forgiving the past

00:52.960 --> 00:54.200
And giving rewards to all

00:54.760 --> 00:55.520
On the other hand

00:56.000 --> 00:58.600
For those who repeatedly disobeyed court orders

00:58.760 --> 01:00.640
Carrying out targeted punishment

01:02.280 --> 01:04.000
Although this was effective

01:04.240 --> 01:07.560
Many of the Prince of Yan's former subordinates, though appearing to submit

01:07.760 --> 01:09.640
Still harbored resentment in their hearts

01:09.920 --> 01:12.320
And after Zhu Yuanzhi was summoned to the capital

01:12.320 --> 01:13.640
And given a nominal position

01:13.640 --> 01:15.600
Became even more closely connected

01:16.480 --> 01:17.680
The fourth year of Taian

01:18.000 --> 01:20.800
Sikong Sheng, in the name of returning to the old capital

01:20.960 --> 01:22.200
Wished to move the capital to Yong'an

01:22.520 --> 01:24.160
Moving the political center north

01:24.360 --> 01:27.880
Met with fierce opposition from Zhu Yuanzhi

01:27.880 --> 01:29.000
United with old friends, noble families, and scholar clans

01:29.000 --> 01:31.640
Finally forced to abandon the plan
